overview: Blondes make a captivating case for your attention in these four obsessive stories from Deeper.com. Stoya directs Rily Steele in a story of willful disobedience between partners in Do You Want. Leah Lee quietly upends her domineering husband's world when he sl--ps in Secret. Adira Allure asks a question whose answer she is unprepared for She Wanted to Knowl Jessa Rhodes is confronted by mroe than the attention she'd bargained for in Show Me Your Legs. Each directs the gaze to exactly the place they want you to look.
title: Blonde Label
